# REPLACE WITH REAL .usdz
#
# Sprint 30 Bucket JJ — placeholder for ARKit Quick Look.
#
# Real .usdz binaries are produced by the `usdz-converter` Cloud Run service
# (see infra/usdz-converter/) from the matching .glb files in this folder's
# parent directory. Apple's `usdzconvert` only runs on macOS; do NOT try to
# generate these locally on Windows/Linux.
#
# Build pipeline: scripts/generate-ar-usdz.mjs invokes the Cloud Run service
# for each kind in PlacedObjectKind and uploads the resulting .usdz to GCS.
# This file exists only so HEAD probes from ArQuickLookButton return 200
# during local dev / smoke tests before the converter runs.
